### VoiceForge — API test suite
### Run with the REST Client extension in VS Code
### Variables — update BASE_URL if running remotely

@base = http://localhost:3000

# ─── 1. Create a voice profile ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name createProfile
POST {{base}}/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Profile",
  "description": "A test voice profile"
}

###

# ─── 2. List profiles ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/profiles

###

# ─── 3. Upload a writing sample ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Replace :profileId with the id returned in step 1
# Use a REST client that supports multipart, or run this curl command:
# curl -F "files=@sample.txt" http://localhost:3000/upload/1

POST {{base}}/upload/1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. Life is short, art is long.
Writing is thinking. Clear sentences come from clear thoughts.

--boundary--

###

# ─── 4. Get profile with samples ────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/profiles/1

###

# ─── 5. Analyse the profile ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/profiles/1/analyse

###

# ─── 6. List writer fragments ───────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/fragments

###

# ─── 7. Rewrite without writer influences ───────────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/rewrite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profileId": 1,
  "text": "Artificial intelligence is a rapidly evolving field that is transforming numerous industries worldwide. The technology has advanced significantly in recent years.",
  "tone": "casual blog post"
}

###

# ─── 8. Rewrite with writer influences ──────────────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/rewrite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profileId": 1,
  "text": "Artificial intelligence is a rapidly evolving field that is transforming numerous industries worldwide. The technology has advanced significantly in recent years.",
  "tone": "casual blog post",
  "writerSlugs": ["hemingway", "orwell"]
}

###

# ─── 9. Rewrite history ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/rewrite/history/1

###

# ─── 10. Update profile name ────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{base}}/profiles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Profile Name"
}

###

# ─── 11. Delete profile ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DELETE {{base}}/profiles/1

###

# ─── Health check ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/health
